description: The FLEXVOLT 60V MAX* 8 1/4 in. table saw is maximized for accuracy, capacity and runtime. The brushless motor delivers the power to cut all co mm.on materials, the rack & pinion fence allows for fast, easy adjustments and provides the capacity to rip 4x8 sheet goods. The DCS7485T1 comes with one FLEXVOLT 20V/60V MAX* battery and fast charger.

Keep using the pneumatic tools you already have while enjoying the convenience and portability of cordless with the 20V MAX* 2-1/2 Gallon Brushless Cordless Air Compressor. Each battery charge can sink over 850 nails**, providing runtime to complete a variety of applications. Its OneTurn™ Regulator means you won’t have to fight with the dial. Plus, it's made right here in the USA with global materials.

Get the job done with up to 65% more power**. The V20* Cordless 4-1/2-in. Small Angle Grinder features a brushless motor that gives you a longer motor life and delivers ultimate power. It’s built with the user in mind, providing control and versatility while adding comfort during use.

Built from composite construction to reduce weight and fatigue, this 750-foot pound impact wrench comes with a number of high-quality features. Wearing mechanics gloves? No problem. A large power adjustment dial is included, along with easy push-button forward and reverse controls. It has 5 total settings with a built-in muffler to reduce noise.

Makita’s 4" x 24" Belt Sander, model 9403, combines power and speed with ease-of-use features and less noise for fast and efficient stock removal. The 9403 is ideal for woodworkers, carpenters, furniture makers, floor installers, deck builders and general contractors who require a best-in-class belt sander. The 9403 features a powerful 11 AMP motor with electronic speed control to maintain constant speed under load, with a 4 wide belt and a speed of 1,640 ft./min. for fast stock removal. The 9403 also features less noise: at only 84dB, it is one of the quietest sanders in its class.
